    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We need to be a bit careful about this.  For some traits we may indeed want to track the aggregate level across multiple types instead of having them tracked separately.  Somebody needs to take charge of this feature and write up something specifying exactly how upgrades and their levels should interact with traits in all the different cases, and then we can work from there.  If we don't, then I expect we will end up chasing regressions for the next release cycle.\n"
