    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Actually, I plan on splitting GainsStatUpgrades into separate traits and have since about the time of the introduction of UpgradableTrait. The problem with GainsStatUpgrades is that it clumps functionality together (fire-power modifier, damage modifier,...). One reason for the bug may be this bad design making functionality non-obvious. If I remember correctly, I'm not the only one who thinks it should be split.\n\nSince GainsStatUpgrades should be replaced with separate traits and this seems to have no other use (so far), This probably should be closed for now at least and possibly an issue opened regarding this functionality to figure out what to do first.\n"
