    "body": "Well, the decision has been implicitly made that upgradable traits will use the sum of all upgrade levels instead of individual upgrade levels. That means that this PR is not needed.\n\nAnd I'm pretty sure #8572 will take care of the problem with `GainsStatUpgrades`. The only thing, that might be needed in the future, is some explicit documentation on the agreements and conventions regarding the upgrade system so that regressions like this don't happen again. But I'm not sure if that even needs its own PR.\n"
